<br>
Its great for quading, since you'll get hit every onceinawhile, especially if your using lumi, and having fungi on with a regen spell will make that a non-factor.  Its nice for groups since you can tell the cleric not to heal you if you do get hit, or only if your really low on hp's, since you hp regen is really that much faster than everybody elses.  Doesnt look half bad either. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utils.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tils</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 131<br> <font color=#333399>(6/20/01 3:30:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3301.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.datacruz.com/~game/tils.jpg height=184 width=125></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .....</span><hr size=1> I have the thurg bp....and use the fungi when i go to old world...all i do is grove myself....swap the bp and put fungi on....then you can manastone all day and be fm most of the time.<br>
